Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.62,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(640,600)}「花坂結衣定下約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡怎麼樣都理解不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真擅長教人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很合適做老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…關於這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的話 以後也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始也請你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才還用得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 突然登門造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就沒水了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停水…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澡堂嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝陪我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…洗好之後能稍微等一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去也想一起什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜風真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在想東京究竟是怎樣的地方 我能好好過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我也能拼一拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各方面都要感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體要變涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.11,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}目の前の扉を開けたら春風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.53,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}鳥たちも樹木で待ち合わせ
