Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:42.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}通往你的信號顯示著天藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}筆直向前吧
